Description: Upward Leaf effect on screen from Maple Treeway; [[AREA type#AREA type 0x01 (EnvEffect)|AREA type 0x01]] activates this object if the first AREA setting is set to 1. Instead of surrounding the player with the particle effect, the object's position is used to create a region in which the effect will occur. This region is loosely 10000un eastward and 10000un above the object's position.
